<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRenderer.InitializationFlags" Title="InitializationFlags enumeration" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRenderer">IRenderer</PageRef> ->
    InitializationFlags
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>InitializationFlags</TypeRef> enumeration is supplied to <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRenderer.Initialize">Initialize</PageRef> when an <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRenderer">IRenderer</PageRef> object is initialized. It is reserved for renderer initialization behaviours that must be selected before resources or render tree nodes are created.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Members">
    <EnumMemberList>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="None">
        Requests standard renderer initialization with no additional initialization flags enabled.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
    </EnumMemberList>
  </Section>
